text: Santo Domingo Norte is a municipality of the Santo Domingo Province in the Dominican Republic. There is one municipal district (distrito municipal) within the municipality: La Victoria. ==Overview== Santo Domingo Norte was created as a municipality in 2001 by Law 163-01 splitting the Santo Domingo province from the Distrito Nacional including those parts of metropolitan Santo Domingo north of the Isabela River. ==See also== *List of municipalities and municipal districts of the Dominican Republic ==References== Category:Populated places in Santo Domingo Province Category:Municipalities of the Dominican Republic
title: Santo Domingo Norte
